title: Keeping Up with Vaccinations
description: Once a child is registered for school, parents have to update their child's immunization record with the health unit each time their child is vaccinated.  This video outlines to parents the link between public health, immunization and their childrens health.
tags: HKPR District Health Unit', 'Your Health Matters', 'immunization', 'school'
